set.seed(123)

# Table
## Distal small intestine
table_lefse_genotypesex_ST2 <- df_all_lefse %>% 
  filter(Tissue == "Distal small intestine") %>%
  mutate(value=ifelse(Abundant_place_Male=="WT",`LDA score (log10)`,
                        ifelse(Abundant_place_Male=="KO", `LDA score (log10)`/(-1),NA))) %>% 
  mutate(label=paste(Family, Genera)) %>% 
  select(Taxa=label, Family, Genera, value, Group=Abundant_place_Male)

table_lefse_genotypesex_arrange_ST2 <- table_lefse_genotypesex_ST2 %>% 
  arrange (desc(value)) %>% 
  select(Family, Genera)

table_lefse_genotypesex_arrange_ST2
## # A tibble: 2 × 2
##   Family             Genera                  
##   <chr>              <chr>                   
## 1 Saccharimonadaceae Candidatus Saccharimonas
## 2 Lachnospiraceae    Unassigned
## Large intestine
table_lefse_genotypesex_LT <- df_all_lefse %>% 
  filter(Tissue == "Large intestine") %>%
  mutate(value=ifelse(Abundant_place_Male=="WT",`LDA score (log10)`,
                        ifelse(Abundant_place_Male=="KO", `LDA score (log10)`/(-1),NA))) %>% 
  mutate(label=paste(Family, Genera)) %>% 
  select(Taxa=label, Family, Genera, value, Group=Abundant_place_Male)

table_lefse_genotypesex_arrange_LT <- table_lefse_genotypesex_LT %>% 
  arrange (desc(value)) %>% 
  select(Family, Genera)

table_lefse_genotypesex_arrange_LT
## # A tibble: 2 × 2
##   Family          Genera       
##   <chr>           <chr>        
## 1 Lachnospiraceae Unassigned   
## 2 Lachnospiraceae Acetatifactor
# Plot
figure_genotypesex_ST2 <- ggplot(data=table_lefse_genotypesex_ST2, aes(x=reorder(Taxa,value),y=value,fill=Group))+
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  coord_flip()+
  theme_bw() +
  labs(title = "", 
       y="LDA score (log 10)")+
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",
        legend.title = element_text(size=10),
        axis.text.x=element_text(colour="black", face="plain", size=25), 
        axis.title.x=element_text(margin = margin(t = 5), size=16),
        axis.title.y = element_blank(),
        axis.title = element_text(face="plain", size = 10),
        plot.title = element_text(size=10, hjust=0.5), # face="bold"
        panel.border = element_blank(),
        aspect.ratio = 0.2,
        plot.background = element_rect(fill="transparent", colour = "transparent"),
        panel.grid = element_blank(),
        axis.text.y=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.y=element_blank()
        )+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(-6,6),breaks = seq(-6,6,1))+
  scale_fill_manual(values=c("#654e3a","#30436d"))

figure_genotypesex_ST2
